  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41332734_6_8788-8850",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8788-8850",
      "markText": "这一时期开启了伊朗人与希伯来人之间的长久同盟，一直持续到7世纪萨珊王朝被穆斯林军队推翻，随后其友谊多次重建，直到巴列维王朝。",
      "totalCount": 414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41332734&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8788&rangeEnd=8850",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532e807276affeb357860?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8788&rangeEnd=8850"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41332734_27_17206-17286",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "17206-17286",
      "markText": "七十年过去了。伊朗人似乎对他不到二十年的统治所记取的只有他们的国家朝进步和繁荣迈出的一大步、良好的社会治安、妇女解放、政教分离，所有这一切都是他光辉业绩的成果。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41332734&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=17206&rangeEnd=17286",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532e807276affeb357860?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=17206&rangeEnd=17286"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41332734_15_7431-7582",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "7431-7582",
      "markText": "他命第一个：“割开你自己的喉咙！”又对第二个下令：“从塔楼顶上跳下去！”二人都毫不迟疑立即执行[26]。然后他对国王的信使说：“告诉你的主人，我有两万个跟他们一样的青年。让他小心为妙！”",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41332734&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=7431&rangeEnd=7582",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532e807276affeb357860?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=7431&rangeEnd=7582"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41332734_15_14504-14568",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "14504-14568",
      "markText": "因此，哈桑·萨巴赫的记忆和思想并不仅仅活在伊朗北部山区的神话和传说中，它们还入侵了影视领域，更充当了某些知名电子游戏的剧情背景。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41332734&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=14504&rangeEnd=14568",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532e807276affeb357860?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=14504&rangeEnd=14568"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41332734_4_6225-6300",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6225-6300",
      "markText": "他命人在一座浮雕上为他的荣耀刻下：“我用一个月将埃兰国化为一片废墟。我消灭了这里人的话语、家禽的吠鸣、鸟儿的歌声。从此，野兽将可以在这里平静地生活。”",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41332734&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6225&rangeEnd=6300",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532e807276affeb357860?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6225&rangeEnd=6300"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41332734_6_6382-6459",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6382-6459",
      "markText": "对居鲁士来说，这是一个体现他全新管理模式的机会：没有征服者，也没有被征服者，有的只是建立在不同族群互尊互敬基础之上的持久联合，而他将是这一切的象征和保人。",
      "totalCount": 196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41332734&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6382&rangeEnd=6459",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532e807276affeb357860?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6382&rangeEnd=6459"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41332734_3_1217-1280",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1217-1280",
      "markText": "世界上很少有国家如伊朗这般经历了如此众多的领土、政治和宗教动荡。曾经多少次人们以为伊朗将在侵略的铁蹄下、在屠杀和政权颠覆中灭亡",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41332734&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1217&rangeEnd=1280",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532e807276affeb357860?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1217&rangeEnd=1280"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41332734_3_1313-1331",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1313-1331",
      "markText": "因为伊朗人拥有一种力量：他们的历史。",
